ck_generate_sTable

ck_generate_sTable.Rd

a perturbation table (for large and small cells) for testing purposes

ck_generate_sTable(smallC = 12, ...)

Arguments

smallC

number of columns for the perturbation table for large cells
...

additional parameters, not yet used

Value

a data.table with 256 rows and 32+smallC columns

Examples

ck_generate_sTable(smallC = 10)
